parameters:
Bunny-chan: Alright, tonight marks the start of Monster
Fight!! Today we have a revenge match between Anomalocaris
Mosman-san and Shark Duke-san♪

Spectator: Shark Duke is just going to lose again... It's
not even worth betting on. I've had my fill of watching him
masturbate all day, so I'll let it slide...

Spectator: That was some intense action... As a token of my
gratitude, I've placed a 500 yen bet on Shark Duke. I hope
he does something erotic again, so part of me wants him to
lose.

Memimi: Damn you... I'll show you... damn it... son of a
bitch...

Anomalocaris Mosman: As expected, by the third time, I'm
getting bored of fighting you! It's about time I engrave the
true terror of my Anomalocaris fangs into you!!

Bunny-chan: Okaaay, 10 seconds to start~ Please get to your
starting positions~ Good luck to both of you~❤︎

Anomalocaris Mosman: Mos mos mos... What's wrong? Your
movements are getting sluggish... Looks like it's going to
be another victory for me!!

Memimi: (No, I can't... lose again...? Will these
embarrassing days continue...? Being shamed throughout the
city... still...? I can't stand it...!!)
Memimi: Ughya... Huh...? It doesn't hurt...

Anomalocaris Mosman: Huh...? There's no impact...? That's
strange... Ahh!!?

Anomalocaris Mosman: Gah-!!? My Anomalocaris fangs have
snapped off!!!

Anomalocaris Mosman: (Damn it... Because I made the fangs
out of plastic, their attack power increased but their
durability...!! Plus, fighting back-to-back battles in a
short period... The material couldn't withstand it...!)

Memimi: I don't know what's going on but... this is my
chance!!!

Anomalocaris Mosman: Ughya----------!!! To be defeated by...
such a little girl, me... collapsing...

Bunny-chan: The victory goes to Shark Duke-san!
Congratulations❤︎

Memimi: I won... Uooooh, I won...!! Thank goodness... I was
so scared... ugh...

Memimi's organization absorbed and merged with Anomalocaris
Mosman's organization, becoming one of the top super
organizations in the city...
